desc: Shop for all your dog needs at The Hungry Dog. We stock a wide range of premium, natural and grain free food and treats. There are no preservatives or nasties in our dog products so we cater for dogs that have sensitive stomachs too.

layout.text: A healthy dog is a happy dog
The best in premium dog food, treats and more. No preservatives, additives and grain free. It’s as natural as you can get.
